            <title>[LU-4299] kernel update [SLES11 SP3 3.0.101-0.8] </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4299</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;New kernel version for SLES11 SP3, 3.0.101-0.8.  Need to update lustre config and build files.  May need to refresh some base kernel patches too, but won&apos;t be able to tell that until we can run a regular build framework build.  The patches apply and build OK in a manual build using quilt, but I think our build system is a bit pickier about patches applying without any fuzz.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;At the moment only the kernel version in SP3 has been bumped, but SP2 may follow in a short time.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
